      "detail": "추가: 가환 군 구조\n\n[functor:free] F: Set→Ab. F(S)=⊕_S ℤ\n[functor:forgetful] U: Ab→Set. F⊣U."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "source": "Set",
      "target": "VectorSpace",
